FBIS3-23244 "jptot011__l94060" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 5 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ALGERIA Television Correspondent Critically Wounded LD0503200294 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 5 Mar 94 LD0503200294 Algiers ENTV Television Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] [correspondent pauses several seconds before speaking] You may wonder why this silence. In all simplicity, it is because I have news that is difficult to convey. Today we are also continuing to count our dead. Yet another colleague and friend, Hacene Benaouda, was shot in the head today in a despicable attack. At this moment, our colleague Hacene is still fighting death in the Maillot hospital in Bab El Oued. [passage omitted]
